      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im working on this script for a dark comedy movie that pokes fun at how hollywood handles different groups. i really dont want to accidentally lean into old tropes and end up being offensive lol. can u help me out and list like 5 common racial stereotypes that movies always use so i know what to stay away from or maybe subvert?",
